OL,3,CWelsh-Made thriller Havoc starring Tom
OL,4,CHardy lands on Netflix
OL,6,FThe biggest feature film shot entirely
OL,7,Fin Wales has landed on Netflix today.
OL,9,FHavoc - an action thriller starring
OL,10,FTom Hardy, and directed by Welsh
OL,11,Ffilmmaker Gareth Evans, is being
OL,12,Fhailed as the biggest feature ever
OL,13,Ffilmed solely in the country,
OL,14,Faccording to the streaming platform.
OL,16,FFilming was spread across South Wales,
OL,17,Fwith a mix of location shoots and
OL,18,Fstudio work in Cardiff and Bridgend.
