OL,3,CWelsh-Made thriller Havoc starring Tom
OL,4,CHardy lands on Netflix
OL,6,FThe crime drama follows a detective
OL,7,Fforced to navigate a dangerous
OL,8,Fcriminal underworld after a deal gone
OL,9,Fwrong.
OL,11,FIts production is one of the latest
OL,12,Fprojects supported by Creative Wales,
OL,13,Fand is part of a wider boom of film-
OL,14,Fmaking across the nation.
OL,16,FFollowing the huge successes of Wales-
OL,17,Fbased productions- like Sex Education
OL,18,F- Netflix say since 2020, these have
OL,19,Finjected more than #200 million into
OL,20,Fthe UK economy, and supported over 500
OL,21,FWelsh businesses.
