OL,3,CWelsh-Made thriller Havoc starring Tom
OL,4,CHardy lands on Netflix
OL,6,FCalling attention to Wales' beautiful
OL,7,Flandscapes, Netflix UK's Vice
OL,8,FPresident of Production, Anna Mallet,
OL,9,Fpraised it as "an amazing place to
OL,10,Fmake entertainment."
OL,12,FIn a further nod to its filming roots,
OL,13,FHavoc is available with Welsh-
OL,14,Fsubtitles, following similiar efforts
OL,15,Fwith The Adam Project starring Ryan
OL,16,FReynolds, and Dal Y Mellt.
